{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-13556/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-13556"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["1:35:56"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["medium shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["eye-level"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["handheld, zoom out"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["group shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A group shares a meal around a table"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13556/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-13556","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13556/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-13556"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13556/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13556/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13556/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13556/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13556/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13556/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13556/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13556/canvas/1/c43a3ff1-66ef-4556-98fa-a6198b1f4f92","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T19:36:15.490Z","creator":"lucia","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>This scene was shot at the restaurant <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW46999218 BCX2\" href=\"https://www.wildhoneylondon.co.uk/wildhoneystjames\"><u>Wild Honey St. James</u></a> in London.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13556/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:67.79220779220786,135.5844155844156,264.93506493506493,96.62337662337663"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13556/canvas/1/1b4a880f-014d-4283-9a42-a913a79f818c","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T19:37:15.940Z","creator":"lucia","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Reynolds, Cyril, and Alma are in the same positions at the table as they were in their <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW101952679 BCX2\" href=\"https://ptannotated.com/items/phan-03316.html\"><u>earlier</u></a> <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW101952679 BCX2\" href=\"https://ptannotated.com/items/phan-03324.html\"><u>dinner</u></a> at the same restaurant. However, Reynolds is now closer to Alma than to Cyril, and Alma is as much a part of the conversation as they are. This similarity emphasizes how their relationship has progressed. While Alma was once on the outskirts of his life, she is now fully a part of his family. The lighting is also much warmer in this scene than it was previously. The House of Woodcock is no longer dead and unchanging; Alma has brought life and light back into Reynolds’s life.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13556/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:571.1688311688313,166.75324675324674,1306.7532467532467,667.012987012987"}}}]}]}]}